Installation Intructions
------------------------

Make sure you have the prerequisites listed below installed. Then,

./configure && make install


Prerequisites
-------------

Python (>=2.6) http://www.python.org/
Cython         http://www.cython.org/
GSL            http://www.gnu.org/software/gsl/
NLopt          http://ab-initio.mit.edu/wiki/index.php/NLopt



Usage
-----

The script 'peakolate' is responsible for performing the scan.

Run, 'peakolate --help' for basic instructions.

the sequencing bias model can be trained with 'peakolate-seqbias'.



